<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.9">
<l>tukkamiṉ ñāṉac cuṭaroḷi mūrtti tuḻāyalaṅ kalperumāṉ</l>
<l>mikkapaṉ māyaṅka ḷālvikir tañceytu vēṇṭu muruvukoṇṭu</l>
<l>nakka pirāṉō ṭayaṉmuta lāka vellāru mevaiyun taṉṉu</l>
<l>ḷokkavo ṭuṅkavi ḻuṅkaval lāṉaippeṟ ṟoṉṟun taḷarvilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great lord with a tulsi garland, [his] form of the glowing light of flawless knowledge,</l>
<l>getting on to him who is capable of swallowing everyone and everything so that they are</l>
<l>equally contained in him, the unborn one along with the smiling lord as the first,</l>
<l>taking the form he wants, causing change by very many illusions, I will be without any slackening.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
